HOW TO RUN AND PLAY -

             Copy the following files into your main c/ directory:
             (find the following files on your AMIGA Workbench disk.)
              
                             ICONX
                             ASSIGN
                             ECHO
                             MAKEDIR
                             COPY
                             DELETE

      Copy all the archive's files onto a disk or anywhere on a hard drive.

      Click on the IB_INSTALL icon.

      This will make an IB drawer and place the files in the right places.



                Ok, no problems?     Good.

                Click on the IB_DEMO icon to start 'er up!

PLAYING THE DEMO -

               Use the joystick to guide Dab, the magic ornament around
               the landscape.

               The first thing to do is look for pieces of paper that are
               on the ground, they will give you information on how to get
               along with the game.

               The FIRE button or SPACEBAR will advance the messages.

               Pressing the fire button will do various things in the game,
               you can use some items you collect by pressing fire and the
               direction you wish to throw/use/place, etc.

               The spacebar on your keyboard will run through the items
               you might have collected, most items have a number next
               to them denoting the amount you have left.

INTERACTIONS -

               There are some object you can't exactly pick up, but you may
               be able to use them or find something in them.
               (Hint: You'll need a key to open chests!)

               You'll have to avoid some parts of the landscape, like
               spikes, holes, water, etc.

GAME PLAY HINTS -

               PLAY LOOSE.
               The only way to play, just be adventurous, go anywhere and
               everywhere!

               There is only one bonus round, in it you have to match the
               symbols in the "slot machine" to match the pattern at the
               top of the screen, to change a symbol you have to hit the
               red button in front of it.

FUNCTION KEYS -

               P  will toggle the ITEM BOX & EXTRA LIVES on/off the screen.

               S  toggles the sound effects ON/OFF.

               M  toggles music ON/OFF.

              <Spacebar>  as explained above, cycles through your items.

               +  press this and it will slow the game down a notch.

               -  this speeds the game back up.

